cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper proposes an image-based end-to-end learning framework for lane-change decisions, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). The framework is designed for autonomous vehicles, which falls under robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses safety concerns, which could be related to cybersecurity (cs.CR).
